{"tid":637734,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★中興救星？內媒：唔用Android可用阿里YunOS","createTime":"2018-04-22T05:55:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-23T00:05:31.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"6ff7a26112e471c427bde574136dd66a9c825407","tid":637734,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T05:55:41.000Z","msg":"美國商務部日前宣布制裁中國電訊設備生產商中興通訊，禁止美國公司向其出售電子技術、通訊元件，為期7年。有報道指，因將無法使用美國公司研發的操作系統，如Android（安卓）等，故制裁或會波及中興的智能手機業務。對此，有內地科技網站日前發文分析，指由內地電商阿里巴巴集團開發的YunOS（雲OS），或可成為中興的救星。<br />\n<br />\n文章指，YunOS是基於電腦作業系統Linux開發。根據媒體前年11月披露的數據顯示，當年中國智能手機操作系統市場，YunOS以14%的市場佔有率，超越美國蘋果的iOS，成為僅次於Android的第二大手機操作系統。這是因為YunOS趕上了四五線城市、農村的換機潮，通過農村包圍城市策略，得以在短期內迅速發展。<br />\n<br />\n文章指出，「因此，如果有一天國產手機無法使用安卓系統，我們還可以三星、阿里巴巴的操作系統，雖然小眾，但集中力量克服應用市場也不是不可以。實在不行，手機廠商也可以結盟自己研發。」但文章亦指出，雖然YunOS在國內發展順利，但在海外或會面臨專利糾紛，這或不利於如中興這樣的外銷品牌使用。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180421/bkncn-20180421204013553-0421_05011_001.html?refer=hn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180421%2Fbkncn-20180421204013553-0421_05011_001.html%3Frefer%3Dhn&d=0HwJE49gAfonorBSzpbb2dibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=26e2e87f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180421/bkncn-20180421204013553-0421_05011_001.html?refer=hn</a>"},{"pid":"4830fe8dc81116039aacccd694ce9e87a4379170","tid":637734,"uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T05:57:11.000Z","msg":"當年中國智能手機操作系統市場，<span style=\"color: red;\">YunOS以14%的市場佔有率，超越美國蘋果的iOS</span>，成為僅次於Android的第二大手機操作系統<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbf15c9522a1af834cad39f93297f0a9b8ffab81","tid":637734,"uid":31237,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T05:58:28.000Z","msg":"電話都可以農村包圍城市 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca5b07731b89387ef31ee6056ec6e8c23cb11c60","tid":637734,"uid":61280,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T06:02:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">YunOS基於Linux開發？？？哈玩文字遊戲真係支狗點都宇宙第一！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nYunOS係Android改出黎小學生都知啦仆街！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"66e55b42c5c8e19b20e0efaaa59fc160f4607fd7","tid":637734,"uid":54733,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T06:02:44.000Z","msg":"Google公司的安迪&middot;魯賓認為YunOS直接使用Android的運行時函式庫、軟體框架及開發工具，可以被視為Android的一個分支，但不完全與Android相容[13]。參與Android的所有開發者，都貢獻了他們的原始碼，但YunOS拒絕與其他人分享，因此不應該被加入Android的生態系統中。YunOS應用中心有許多盜版的Android軟體下載，有些軟體更由Google開發[14]。<br />\n<br />\n此外，雖然YunOS使用了開源化的Linux操作系統，但是，YunOS也未依GPL的精神與條款，將原始代碼公開釋出，因此也不被Linux社群認可是合法的Linux分支。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1e36c3dd5c57f57ea6b80935e3aa739f10dd355","tid":637734,"uid":130105,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T06:03:47.000Z","msg":"即係大陸rom<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a041712561e7467467d38040de8cf0bfe5208e6a","tid":637734,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T06:05:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>即係大陸rom<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">ROM同OS係兩樣野！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"29e6d3b6f3ee06b152c0ffaf813d51088b91cc52","tid":637734,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66e55b42c5c8e19b20e0efaaa59fc160f4607fd7","tid":637734,"u